{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312034040990090273d8849ee","session_id":"e8c5e130-cc78-4ab4-9f64-924bbfd756be","message":{"id":"20260312034040990090273d8849ee","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde6a72d69f73a81ac88ee3c8122b","name":"Task","input":{"description":"PM: Fix CRITICAL analyze issues","prompt":"Read /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.codebuddy/agents/prizm-dev-team-pm.md. You need to fix CRITICAL issues found in prizmkit.analyze for feature F-004.\n\n**CRITICAL Issues to Fix:**\n\n**F01 - Lock Mechanism Conflict:**\n- spec.md L221 (D1) requires \"文件锁 + PID 校验\" \n- plan.md L430 uses \"in-memory mutex\"\n- In-memory mutex cannot satisfy AC-7.3 (auto-release on process crash)\n- **Resolution**: Update plan.md Decision Log to use file-based lock + PID verification to match spec\n\n**F02 - Module Naming Conflict:**\n- spec.md L163 uses `pipeline-controller.js`\n- plan.md L65 and tasks.md use `process-controller.js`\n- **Resolution**: Update spec.md Scope Boundaries to use `process-controller.js` to match plan/tasks\n\n**HIGH Issues to also address:**\n\n**F03 - User Story Mapping Table Misalignment:**\n- plan.md L293-301 has incorrect US mappings\n- Correct mappings should be: US-2→Stop, US-3→Retry, US-5→Status, US-6→Logs, US-7→Concurrency, US-8→Error, US-9→Integration\n\n**F04 & F05 - NFR Coverage Gaps:**\n- NFR-1 Performance testing (<100ms, <50ms, <200ms) has no dedicated task\n- NFR-2 Reliability testing has no validation task\n- Add tasks or extend existing tasks to cover these\n\nFiles to edit:\n- .prizmkit/specs/004-pipeline-process-controller/spec.md\n- .prizmkit/specs/004-pipeline-process-controller/plan.md\n- .prizmkit/specs/004-pipeline-process-controller/tasks.md\n\nMake the necessary corrections and report completion.","subagent_type":"prizm-dev-team-pm","team_name":"prizm-dev-team"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":33659,"output_tokens":560,"cach