ile: .prizm-docs/pipeline.prizm\n 155→- [ ] [T-902] Add JSDoc comments to all public methods — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n 156→- [ ] [T-903] [P] Add JSDoc to lock-manager — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n 157→- [ ] [T-904] [P] Add JSDoc to state-manager — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n 158→- [ ] [T-905] Performance test for log reading with large files — file: tests/performance/\n 159→- [ ] [T-906] Edge case: Handle corrupted state files — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n 160→- [ ] [T-907] Edge case: Handle permission errors on lock files — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n 161→- [ ] [T-908] Update REGISTRY.md with F-004 entry — file: .prizmkit/specs/REGISTRY.md\n 162→- [ ] [T-909] Final code review and cleanup — file: src/\n 163→\n 164→---\n 165→\n 166→## Summary\n 167→\n 168→| Phase | Task Range | Count | Parallelizable |\n 169→|-------|------------|-------|----------------|\n 170→| Setup | T-001 ~ T-009 | 9 | 4 |\n 171→| Foundational | T-010 ~ T-069 | 48 | 12 |\n 172→| User Stories | T-100 ~ T-199 | 71 | 20 |\n 173→| Polish | T-900 ~ T-909 | 10 | 3 |\n 174→| **Total** | | **138** | **39** |\n 175→\n 176→---\n 177→\n 178→## Dependency Graph\n 179→\n 180→```\n 181→T-001 ──┬──> T-018, T-019, T-020\n 182→        │\n 183→T-002 ──┼──> T-039, T-040, T-041\n 184→        │\n 185→T-003 ──┴──> T-057, T-107, T-108, ...\n 186→\n 187→T-004 ─────> T-005, T-054\n 188→\n 189→T-009 ─────> T-011, T-031\n 190→\n 191→T-010 ~ T-020 (Lock Manager) ──> T-100, T-170\n 192→T-030 ~ T-041 (State Manager) ──> T-150, T-160\n 193→T-050 ~ T-057 (Controller Skeleton) ──> T-100+\n 194→\n 195→T-100 ~ T-119 (US-1) ──> T-190\n 196→T-120 ~ T-126 (US-2) ──> T-190\n 197→T-130 ~ T-135 (US-3) ──> T-190\n 198→...\n 199→```\n 200→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde6a72d69f73a81ac88ee3c8122b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:40:56.079Z","_requestId":"e21d0cf101524861bfec5442101833c9"}
