{"type":"user","uuid":"6541e88e-ff13-4028-90dd-b4972b3b94db","session_id":"e8c5e130-cc78-4ab4-9f64-924bbfd756be","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde6bdc3a43d7877cf1f21486d9a5","content":[{"type":"text","text":" 158→---\n 159→\n 160→## Scope Boundaries\n 161→\n 162→### In Scope\n 163→- Pipeline 控制器核心模块 (`src/services/process-controller.js`)\n 164→- 并发锁管理器 (`src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js`)\n 165→- 状态管理器 (`src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js`)\n 166→- 错误码扩展 (`src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js`)\n 167→- 与现有 daemon 脚本的集成\n 168→- 单元测试与集成测试\n 169→\n 170→### Out of Scope\n 171→- Telegram 命令路由实现（已在 F-002 完成）\n 172→- Pipeline 内部逻辑修改\n 173→- Web UI\n 174→- 数据库持久化（继续使用 JSON 文件）\n 175→- 认证授权（由上层路由处理）\n 176→\n 177→---\n 178→\n 179→## Dependencies\n 180→\n 181→| Dependency | Type | Status | Notes |\n 182→|------------|------|--------|-------|\n 183→| F-001 | Feature | completed | 提供基础架构 (script-runner, error-codes, path-policy) |\n 184→| F-002 | Feature | completed | 提供命令路由层 (将调用 F-004 API) |\n 185→| launch-daemon.sh | Script | existing | Feature daemon 管理脚本 |\n 186→| launch-bugfix-daemon.sh | Script | existing | Bugfix daemon 管理脚本 |\n 187→| retry-feature.sh | Script | existing | Feature 重试脚本 |\n 188→| retry-bug.sh | Script | existing | Bugfix 重试脚本 |\n 189→\n 190→---\n 191→\n 192→## Risks\n 193→\n 194→| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n 195→|------|-------------|--------|------------|\n 196→| 并发锁实现复杂导致死锁 | Medium | High | 使用简单的文件锁 + PID 检测，避免复杂同步原语 |\n 197→| Daemon 脚本输出格式变化 | Low | Medium | 建立脚本输出契约，添加输出解析测试 |\n 198→| 大日志文件读取阻塞 | Low | Medium | 使用流式读取或限制读取行数 |\n 199→| 跨平台兼容性（macOS/Linux） | Low | Low | 主要使用 Node.js API，脚本在 WSL/Git Bash 兼容 |\n 200→\n 201→---\n 202→\n 203→## Technical Notes\n 204→\n 205→### 现有基础设施\n 206→- `script-runner.js` 已提供基本的命令执行和错误映射\n 207→- `pipeline-control-service.js` 已提供基础 API，但缺少并发保护和 daemon 模式\n 208→- `launch-daemon.sh` 和 `launch-bugfix-daemon.sh` 提供 PID 管理和日志合并\n 209→\n 210→### 设计方向\n 211→- 扩展 `pipeline-control-service.js` 或创建新模块 `process-controller.js`\n 212→- 锁管理器使用文件锁 (`flock` 或 `.lock` 文件 + PID 校验)\n 213→- 状态管理器读取现有的 `pipeline.json` 和 `.pipeline-meta.json`\n 214→\n 215→---\n 216→\n 217→## Decisions\n 218→\n 219→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 220→|----|------|----------|\n 221→| D1 | 2026-03-12 | 使用文件锁 + PID 校验实现并发保护，避免引入外部依赖 |\n 222→| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 创建独立的 `process-controller.js` 模块，而非扩展现有 `pipeline-control-service.js`，以保持职责清晰 |\n 223→| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 复用现有 daemon 脚本的输出格式，不做脚本修改 |\n 224→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde6a72d69f73a81ac88ee3c8122b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:42:18.845Z","_requestId":"e21d0cf101524861bfec5442101833c9"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"05e6fcb5-17ee-4053-9d16-616bb762d2cf","session_id":"e8c5e130-cc78-4ab4-9f64-924bbfd756be","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde6bdef51ad0c670ec26f25575be","content":[{"type":"text","text":" 555→\n 556→## 8. User Story to Component Mapping\n 557→\n 558→| User Story | Primary Component | Supporting Components |\n 559→|------------|-------------------|----------------------|\n 560→| US-1: Unified Pipeline Start | pipeline-controller.startPipeline() | lock-manager, script-runner |\n 561→| US-2: Pipeline Stop | pipeline-controller.stopPipeline() | state-manager, lock-manager |\n 562→| US-3: Target Retry | pipeline-controller.retryTarget() | script-runner, state-manager |\n 563→| US-4: Run Single Feature | pipeline-controller.runSingle() | script-runner |\n 564→| US-5: Status Query | pipeline-controller.getStatus() | state-manager, lock-manager |\n 565→| US-6: Logs Query | pipeline-controller.getLogs() | state-manager |\n 566→| US-7: Concurrency Protection | lock-manager | state-manager |\n 567→| US-8: Error Mapping | error-codes.js (extended) | pipeline-controller |\n 568→| US-9: Telegram Handler Integration | pipeline-controller API design | All |\n 569→\n 570→**Mapping Notes:**\n 571→- US-2 → stopPipeline: 停止守护进程\n 572→- US-3 → retryTarget: 重试失败目标\n 573→- US-5 → getStatus: 状态查询\n 574→- US-6 → getLogs: 日志查询\n 575→- US-7 → lock-manager: 并发保护\n 576→- US-8 → error-codes.js: 错误映射\n 577→- US-9 → API design: Telegram 集成\n 578→\n 579→---\n 580→\n 581→## 9. Implementation Phases\n 582→\n 583→### Phase 1: Foundation (T-001 ~ T-009)\n 584→- Setup test infrastructure\n 585→- Extend error codes\n 586→- Create lock-manager\n 587→- Create state-manager\n 588→\n 589→### Phase 2: Core Controller (T-010 ~ T-099)\n 590→- Implement pipeline-controller skeleton\n 591→- Implement each API method\n 592→- Integrate with existing script-runner\n 593→\n 594→### Phase 3: User Story Implementation (T-100+)\n 595→- US-1: startPipeline\n 596→- US-2: stopPipeline\n 597→- US-3: retryTarget\n 598→- US-4: runSingle\n 599→- US-5: getStatus\n 600→- US-6: getLogs\n 601→- US-7: Lock integration\n 602→- US-8: Error mapping\n 603→- US-9: Integration tests\n 604→\n 605→### Phase 4: Polish (T-900+)\n 606→- Documentation updates\n 607→- Performance optimization\n 608→- Edge case handling\n 609→\n 610→---\n 611→\n 612→## 10. Key Decisions\n 613→\n 614→| ID | Decision | Rationale |\n 615→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde6a72d69f73a81ac88ee3c8122b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:42:18.845Z","_requestId":"e21d0cf101524861bfec5442101833c9"}
