ntracts\n  40→- request validation must reject unknown pipelineType/action and missing targetId for retry/reset\n  41→\n  42→DECISIONS:\n  43→- 2026-03-10 | f001-js-path-policy | include explicit daemon log policy resolver for US2 coverage\n  44→- 2026-03-10 | f001-runner-actions | treat logs/reset as first-class runner actions for US3 coverage\n  45→- 2026-03-12 | f001-feature-complete | all US1-US4 acceptance criteria verified via integration tests\n  46→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde6da49815e71514cd1d7dc7d1dd","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:44:48.089Z","_requestId":"e21d0cf101524861bfec5442101833c9"}
