{"type":"user","uuid":"570b61e7-40f0-4881-b06c-98ed5bb19151","session_id":"e8c5e130-cc78-4ab4-9f64-924bbfd756be","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde7cedda175f56d631bdcbf445ff","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-004: Pipeline Process Controller\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→构建 pipeline 进程控制层，统一封装 dev-pipeline/run.sh 与 run-bugfix.sh 的启动、停止、重试、单特性执行与后台守护模式。该层提供稳定 API 给 Telegram 命令路由调用，并负责并发锁、超时、退出码映射与异常恢复。目标是把当前\"终端操作脚本\"能力抽象为\"程序可调用控制接口\"。\n   6→\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→## User Stories\n  10→\n  11→### US-1: Unified Pipeline Start\n  12→\n  13→**As a** Telegram 用户或系统集成者  \n  14→**I want** 通过统一的控制接口启动 feature pipeline 或 bugfix pipeline  \n  15→**So that** 我不需要关心底层脚本的差异，且能获得标准化的执行结果\n  16→\n  17→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  18→- AC-1.1: `startPipeline({ type: 'feature' | 'bugfix', targetId?, listPath?, daemon?: boolean })` 可启动指定类型管道\n  19→- AC-1.2: 返回结构化结果 `{ ok, runId, pid?, message, errorCode? }`\n  20→- AC-1.3: 若指定 `daemon: true`，以后台守护模式启动，返回 PID\n  21→- AC-1.4: 若管道已在运行中（并发锁检查失败），返回 `LOCK_ACQUISITION_FAILED` 错误\n  22→\n  23→---\n  24→\n  25→### US-2: Pipeline Stop\n  26→\n  27→**As a** 运维人员  \n  28→**I want** 通过控制接口停止正在运行的管道  \n  29→**So that** 我可以从 Telegram 或 API 中止异常的管道执行\n  30→\n  31→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  32→- AC-2.1: `stopPipeline({ type: 'feature' | 'bugfix' })` 可停止指定类型的守护进程\n  33→- AC-2.2: 若进程已停止，返回 `ALREADY_STOPPED` 状态而非错误\n  34→- AC-2.3: 停止操作有 10 秒超时，超时后强制终止\n  35→- AC-2.4: 返回结构化结果 `{ ok, previousPid, message }`\n  36→\n  37→---\n  38→\n  39→### US-3: Target Retry\n  40→\n  41→**As a** 开发者  \n  42→**I want** 重试某个失败的 feature 或 bugfix 目标  \n  43→**So that** 我可以针对单个失败项进行修复而不影响其他已完成的工作\n  44→\n  45→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  46→- AC-3.1: `retryTarget({ type, targetId, listPath? })` 可重试指定目标\n  47→- AC-3.2: 若目标不存在或状态不允许可重试，返回明确错误\n  48→- AC-3.3: 支持前台和后台模式\n  49→- AC-3.4: 返回结构化结果 `{ ok, targetId, message }`\n  50→\n  51→---\n  52→\n  53→### US-4: Run Single Feature\n  54→\n  55→**As a** 开发者  \n  56→**I want** 单独运行某个特定的 feature 或 bugfix  \n  57→**So that** 我可以测试或调试单个工作项而不运行整个队列\n  58→\n  59→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  60→- AC-4.1: `runSingle({ type, targetId, listPath? })` 可执行单个目标\n  61→- AC-4.2: 执行完成后返回完整的执行结果（含 stdout/stderr）\n  62→- AC-4.3: 支持超时配置\n  63→- AC-4.4: 不影响管道整体状态（独立执行）\n  64→\n  65→---\n  66→\n  67→### US-5: Status Query\n  68→\n  69→**As a** 运维人员  \n  70→**I want** 查询管道的当前状态  \n  71→**So that** 我可以了解系统运行情况并做出决策\n  72→\n  73→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  74→- AC-5.1: `getPipelineStatus({ type })` 返回管道状态对象\n  75→- AC-5.2: 状态对象包含 `{ isRunning, pid?, currentFeature?, startedAt?, lastResult? }`\n  76→- AC-5.3: 若有运行中的目标，包含 `currentFeature` 和 `startedAt`\n  77→- AC-5.4: 若无运行中管道，返回 `lastResult`（最近一次执行结果）\n  78→\n  79→---\n  80→\n  81→### US-6: Logs Query\n  82→\n  83→**As a** 运维人员  \n  84→**I want** 获取管道执行日志  \n  85→**So that** 我可以诊断问题或监控执行进度\n  86→\n  87→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  88→- AC-6.1: `getPipelineLogs({ type, lines?: number })` 返回日志内容\n  89→- AC-6.2: 默认返回最近 100 行，可通过 `lines` 参数调整\n  90→- AC-6.3: 日志不存在时返回空字符串而非错误\n  91→- AC-6.4: 返回结构化结果 `{ ok, logs, logPath }`\n  92→\n  93→---\n  94→\n  95→### US-7: Concurrency Protection\n  96→\n  97→**As a** 系统管理员  \n  98→**I want** 防止多个管道实例同时运行  \n  99→**So that** 系统资源不被过度占用且状态文件不会冲突\n 100→\n 101→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n 102→- AC-7.1: 同类型管道同一时间只能有一个实例运行\n 103→- AC-7.2: 锁获取失败时返回 `LOCK_ACQUISITION_FAILED` 错误，含当前持有者信息\n 104→- AC-7.3: 锁在进程异常退出时自动释放（通过 PID 检测）\n 105→- AC-7.4: 提供 `forceUnlock({ type })` 用于强制释放锁（管理员操作）\n 106→\n 107→---\n 108→\n 109→### US-8: Error Mapping\n 110→\n 111→**As a** Telegram handler 开发者  \n 112→**I want** 所有错误都有结构化的错误码和消息  \n 113→**So that** 我可以向用户展示友好的错误提示而非原始错误堆栈\n 114→\n 115→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n 116→- AC-8.1: 所有错误返回 `{ ok: false, errorCode: string, message: string, hint?: string }`\n 117→- AC-8.2: 错误码覆盖: `LOCK_ACQUISITION_FAILED`, `SCRIPT_NOT_FOUND`, `EXEC_TIMEOUT`, `EXEC_FAILED`, `INVALID_TARGET`, `PIPELINE_NOT_RUNNING`, `ALREADY_STOPPED`\n 118→- AC-8.3: 超时错误包含超时时长信息\n 119→- AC-8.4: 脚本缺失错误包含脚本路径\n 120→\n 121→---\n 122→\n 123→### US-9: Telegram Handler Integration\n 124→\n 125→**As a** Telegram bot 开发者  \n 126→**I want** 控制层接口可直接被 Telegram handler 调用  \n 127→**So that** 命令路由实现变得简单且不依赖终端交互\n 128→\n 129→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n 130→- AC-9.1: 所有方法返回 Promise，可被 async/await 调用\n 131→- AC-9.2: 无需传递 process.stdin/stdout 依赖\n 132→- AC-9.3: 执行结果可通过 JSON 序列化传输\n 133→- AC-9.4: 提供 `createPipelineController()` 工厂函数，支持依赖注入\n 134→\n 135→---\n 136→\n 137→## Non-Functional Requirements\n 138→\n 139→### NFR-1: Performance\n 140→- 控制接口响应时间 < 100ms（不含脚本执行时间）\n 141→- 状态查询 < 50ms\n 142→- 日志读取（100 行）< 200ms\n 143→\n 144→### NFR-2: Reliability\n 145→- 锁机制可靠性 > 99.9%（无死锁场景）\n 146→- 进程异常退出时资源清理率 100%\n 147→\n 148→### NFR-3: Maintainability\n 149→- 核心模块单文件，函数长度 < 100 行\n 150→- 错误码定义在单一文件中管理\n 151→- 测试覆盖率 > 90%\n 152→\n 153→### NFR-4: Extensibility\n 154→- 支持未来添加新的 pipeline 类型（如 `planner`）\n 155→- 错误码可扩展\n 156→- 状态模型可扩展\n 157→\n 158→---\n 159→\n 160→## Scope Boundaries\n 161→\n 162→### In Scope\n 163→- Pipeline 控制器核心模块 (`src/services/process-controller.js`)\n 164→- 并发锁管理器 (`src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js`)\n 165→- 状态管理器 (`src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js`)\n 166→- 错误码扩展 (`src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js`)\n 167→- 与现有 daemon 脚本的集成\n 168→- 单元测试与集成测试\n 169→\n 170→### Out of Scope\n 171→- Telegram 命令路由实现（已在 F-002 完成）\n 172→- Pipeline 内部逻辑修改\n 173→- Web UI\n 174→- 数据库持久化（继续使用 JSON 文件）\n 175→- 认证授权（由上层路由处理）\n 176→\n 177→---\n 178→\n 179→## Dependencies\n 180→\n 181→| Dependency | Type | Status | Notes |\n 182→|------------|------|--------|-------|\n 183→| F-001 | Feature | completed | 提供基础架构 (script-runner, error-codes, path-policy) |\n 184→| F-002 | Feature | completed | 提供命令路由层 (将调用 F-004 API) |\n 185→| launch-daemon.sh | Script | existing | Feature daemon 管理脚本 |\n 186→| launch-bugfix-daemon.sh | Script | existing | Bugfix daemon 管理脚本 |\n 187→| retry-feature.sh | Script | existing | Feature 重试脚本 |\n 188→| retry-bug.sh | Script | existing | Bugfix 重试脚本 |\n 189→\n 190→---\n 191→\n 192→## Risks\n 193→\n 194→| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n 195→|------|-------------|--------|------------|\n 196→| 并发锁实现复杂导致死锁 | Medium | High | 使用简单的文件锁 + PID 检测，避免复杂同步原语 |\n 197→| Daemon 脚本输出格式变化 | Low | Medium | 建立脚本输出契约，添加输出解析测试 |\n 198→| 大日志文件读取阻塞 | Low | Medium | 使用流式读取或限制读取行数 |\n 199→| 跨平台兼容性（macOS/Linux） | Low | Low | 主要使用 Node.js API，脚本在 WSL/Git Bash 兼容 |\n 200→\n 201→---\n 202→\n 203→## Technical Notes\n 204→\n 205→### 现有基础设施\n 206→- `script-runner.js` 已提供基本的命令执行和错误映射\n 207→- `pipeline-control-service.js` 已提供基础 API，但缺少并发保护和 daemon 模式\n 208→- `launch-daemon.sh` 和 `launch-bugfix-daemon.sh` 提供 PID 管理和日志合并\n 209→\n 210→### 设计方向\n 211→- 扩展 `pipeline-control-service.js` 或创建新模块 `process-controller.js`\n 212→- 锁管理器使用文件锁 (`flock` 或 `.lock` 文件 + PID 校验)\n 213→- 状态管理器读取现有的 `pipeline.json` 和 `.pipeline-meta.json`\n 214→\n 215→---\n 216→\n 217→## Decisions\n 218→\n 219→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 220→|----|------|----------|\n 221→| D1 | 2026-03-12 | 使用文件锁 + PID 校验实现并发保护，避免引入外部依赖 |\n 222→| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 创建独立的 `process-controller.js` 模块，而非扩展现有 `pipeline-control-service.js`，以保持职责清晰 |\n 223→| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 复用现有 daemon 脚本的输出格式，不做脚本修改 |\n 224→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde7cedda175f56d631bdcbf445ff","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:00:57.162Z","_requestId":"e21d0cf101524861bfec5442101833c9"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"9e64a02b-b733-45a5-bc05-513154ac6c92","session_id":"e8c5e130-cc78-4ab4-9f64-924bbfd756be","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde7cef9fb1b2c55af3a5de4dbf70","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-004: Pipeline Process Controller — Task List\n   2→\n   3→## Phase 1: Setup (T-001 ~ T-009)\n   4→\n   5→- [x] [T-001] Create test file structure for F-004 — file: tests/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.test.js\n   6→- [x] [T-002] [P] Create state-manager test file — file: tests/pipeline-infra/state-manager.test.js\n   7→- [x] [T-003] [P] Create pipeline-controller test file — file: tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js\n   8→- [x] [T-004] Extend error-codes.js with new F-004 error codes — file: src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js\n   9→- [x] [T-005] [P] Update error-codes tests for new codes — file: tests/pipeline-infra/error-codes.test.js\n  10→- [x] [T-006] Create integration test skeleton — file: tests/integration/f004-pipeline-controller.integration.test.js\n  11→- [x] [T-007] Update .prizm-docs/runtime/pipeline-infra.prizm with new modules — file: .prizm-docs/runtime/pipeline-infra.prizm\n  12→- [x] [T-008] [P] Update .prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm with pipeline-controller — file: .prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm\n  13→- [x] [T-009] Create path policy helpers for lock files and last-result — file: src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js\n  14→\n  15→---\n  16→\n  17→## Phase 2: Foundational (T-010 ~ T-099)\n  18→\n  19→### Lock Manager (T-010 ~ T-029)\n  20→\n  21→- [x] [T-010] Implement createLockManager factory function — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  22→- [x] [T-011] Implement acquireLock with atomic file write — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  23→- [x] [T-012] Implement releaseLock — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  24→- [x] [T-013] Implement isLocked check — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  25→- [x] [T-014] Implement validateLock with PID alive check — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  26→- [x] [T-015] Implement forceUnlock for admin operations — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  27→- [x] [T-016] Implement getLockInfo — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  28→- [x] [T-017] Add stale lock cleanup logic — file: src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js\n  29→- [x] [T-018] [P] Write unit tests for acquireLock/releaseLock — file: tests/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.test.js\n  30→- [x] [T-019] [P] Write unit tests for isLocked/validateLock — file: tests/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.test.js\n  31→- [x] [T-020] [P] Write unit tests for forceUnlock/getLockInfo — file: tests/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.test.js\n  32→\n  33→### State Manager (T-030 ~ T-049)\n  34→\n  35→- [x] [T-030] Implement createStateManager factory function — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  36→- [x] [T-031] Implement readDaemonMeta — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  37→- [x] [T-032] Implement readPipelineState — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  38→- [x] [T-033] Implement readCurrentSession — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  39→- [x] [T-034] Implement getLastResult — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  40→- [x] [T-035] Implement writeDaemonMeta — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  41→- [x] [T-036] Implement writeLastResult — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  42→- [x] [T-037] Implement isDaemonRunning with PID check — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  43→- [x] [T-038] Implement getDaemonPid — file: src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js\n  44→- [x] [T-039] [P] Write unit tests for read operations — file: tests/pipeline-infra/state-manager.test.js\n  45→- [x] [T-040] [P] Write unit tests for write operations — file: tests/pipeline-infra/state-manager.test.js\n  46→- [x] [T-041] [P] Write unit tests for isDaemonRunning/getDaemonPid — file: tests/pipeline-infra/state-manager.test.js\n  47→\n  48→### Pipeline Controller Skeleton (T-050 ~ T-069)\n  49→\n  50→- [x] [T-050] Create pipeline-controller.js with factory function — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  51→- [x] [T-051] Implement dependency injection in createPipelineController — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  52→- [x] [T-052] Implement _acquireLock internal method — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  53→- [x] [T-053] Implement _releaseLock internal method — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  54→- [x] [T-054] Add buildError helper for consistent error formatting — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  55→- [x] [T-055] Add buildResult helper for success responses — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  56→- [x] [T-056] Export default service instance — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  57→- [x] [T-057] [P] Write unit tests for factory and helpers — file: tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js\n  58→\n  59→---\n  60→\n  61→## Phase 3: User Stories (T-100+)\n  62→\n  63→### US-1: Unified Pipeline Start (T-100 ~ T-119)\n  64→\n  65→- [x] [T-100] Implement startPipeline skeleton — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  66→- [x] [T-101] Add lock acquisition in startPipeline — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  67→- [x] [T-102] Implement daemon mode start (launch-daemon.sh) — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  68→- [x] [T-103] Implement foreground mode start (run.sh) — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  69→- [x] [T-104] Add targetId support in startPipeline — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  70→- [x] [T-105] Return structured result with runId/pid — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  71→- [x] [T-106] Handle LOCK_ACQUISITION_FAILED error — file: src/services/pipeline-controller.js\n  72→- [x] [T-107] [P] Write unit tests for startPipeline daemon mode — file: tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js\n  73→- [x] [T-108] [P] Write unit tests for startPipeline foreground mode — file: tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js\n  74→- [x] [T-109] Write inte